Description: OneFinity CNC Controller Firmware
 Complete firmware package for OneFinity CNC controllers including:
  - Web-based control interface (HTTP frontend)
  - Python-based machine control backend
  - AVR firmware for hardware communication
  - System configuration and management scripts
 .
 Supports Raspberry Pi 5 (ARM64) only.
